snippet.title: Sticking with US
snippet.description:
Welcome to my Channel - 

This is a new adventure for me.   Glad you stopped by and I hope you subscribe.   I may not be perfect in my videos, as I am still learning.  Other artists out there make this look very easy.   KUDOS to you!  Hopefully one day - I can grow up to be just like you.  That is a huge compliment to my role models.   

My girls mean the world to me.   I started this adventure to show my girls...you can do anything you put your heart into!  AND at any age.  

To stop SAYING and start DOING! 

Enjoy and thanks for having fun with me.

Fawne
